      * Varible for
     D WSUSER          S             10
     D KUNDNA          S              8
     D KUNDN           S              8  0
     D DELSYSTEM       S              1
     D JSONstring      S          32000
     D Error           S            150
     D AntLest         S              9  0
      *get input-string
      /copy syspeds/qrpgsrcpy,prolog3

      * Parse input
     C                   exsr      Parse
